body:
### expected behaviour

using the external storage ui
mounting storage from the menu

mounting google drive and dropbox storage should mount (green status should be showing) folders should be showing and accessible


### actual behaviour

using the external storage ui
oc requests access from both google drive and dropbox which is granted .
red status is shown for google drive and dropbox
no folders are shown from the files menu

error in log

debug	 core	 include path for class "oc_external" starts with "apps/"	 
warning	 php	 undefined index: \\oc\\files\\storage\\google 
warning	 php	 undefined index: \\oc\\files\\storage\\dropbox

### steps to reproduce
1. dismount drives 
2. reattached drives

### server configuration

hosted at owncube.com

### owncloud version:

5.0.4

### client configuration
browser: chrome

operating system: mac osx 10.8

